#  4 Dolosigranulum pigrum                      32      23            23             55          1.72
#  5 Corynebacterium propinquum                 13       5             5             18          1.38
#  6 Rothia sp902373285                          8       2             2             10          1.25
#  7 Moraxella catarrhalis                     149      26            22            171          1.15
#  8 Streptococcus mitis                       141      21            21            162          1.15
#  9 Staphylococcus aureus                     152      15             3            155          1.02
# 10 Streptococcus pneumoniae                  745      12             7            752          1.01
